00:09:05.530 --> 00:09:07.120
about mate choice.

00:09:07.120 --> 00:09:10.530
You know, some of the primary criteria

00:09:10.530 --> 00:09:14.440
that studies show men and women use

00:09:14.440 --> 00:09:16.170
in order to select mates,

00:09:16.170 --> 00:09:20.240
both, shall we call them transient mates

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:22.300
as well as lifetime mates?

00:09:22.300 --> 00:09:23.990
- Right, well, that's
a critical distinction,

00:09:23.990 --> 00:09:25.720
because what people look for

00:09:25.720 --> 00:09:28.030
in a long-term committed mateship,

00:09:28.030 --> 00:09:31.260
like a marriage partner or a
long-term romantic relationship

00:09:31.260 --> 00:09:33.400
is different from what people look for

00:09:33.400 --> 00:09:35.280
in a hookup or casual sex,

00:09:35.280 --> 00:09:37.993
or one night stand, or
