00:12:02.450 --> 00:12:05.240
And so the logic there is very simple,

00:12:05.240 --> 00:12:06.940
but also very powerful.

00:12:06.940 --> 00:12:10.930
And that is that whatever
qualities are desired,

00:12:10.930 --> 00:12:12.120
consensually desired,

00:12:12.120 --> 00:12:14.220
if there's some heritable basis to those,

00:12:14.220 --> 00:12:17.260
then those increase in
frequency over time.

00:12:17.260 --> 00:12:19.770
And so, and in the human case,

00:12:19.770 --> 00:12:24.510
these two causal processes
of sexual selection

00:12:24.510 --> 00:12:26.410
are related to each other,

00:12:26.410 --> 00:12:29.670
in that the preferences, the
mate preferences of one sex

00:12:29.670 --> 00:12:33.160
basically set the ground
rules for competition

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:34.290
in the opposite sex.

00:12:34.290 --> 00:12:36.120
So if, for example,

00:12:36.120 --> 00:12:39.490
