00:12:52.100 --> 00:12:54.340
and then displaying that their willingness

00:12:54.340 --> 00:12:56.180
to commit that to a particular woman.

00:12:56.180 --> 00:12:57.780
And same with women though.

00:12:57.780 --> 00:13:00.780
One of the interesting things about humans

00:13:00.780 --> 00:13:03.170
is that we have mutual mate choice,

00:13:03.170 --> 00:13:05.620
which is not true in all species.

00:13:05.620 --> 00:13:08.990
And that is that it's not
just a matter of, you know,

00:13:08.990 --> 00:13:11.710
you selecting someone to be your mate,

00:13:11.710 --> 00:13:13.960
they have to reciprocally select you.

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:16.623
And so with mutual mate choice,

00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:20.850
we have both preferences,
mate preferences,

00:13:20.850 --> 00:13:24.200
that women have, and mate
preferences that men have,

00:13:24.200 --> 00:13:27.070
and consequently competition among men

00:13:27.070 --> 00:13:29.660
for access to the most desirable women

00:13:29.660 --> 00:13:31.790
in competition among women for access

00:13:31.790 --> 00:13:33.870
to the most desirable man.

00:13:33.870 --> 00:13:37.420
So that's sort of a little
