00:27:28.540 --> 00:27:31.180
Well, as I mentioned,

00:27:31.180 --> 00:27:34.897
it's a reciprocal mutual
mate choice phenomenon.

00:27:34.897 --> 00:27:36.790
- She constraints the equation.

00:27:36.790 --> 00:27:37.960
- Well, she constrains it,

00:27:37.960 --> 00:27:41.080
but also a marriage and long-term mating

00:27:41.080 --> 00:27:44.810
are things other than reproductive unions

00:27:44.810 --> 00:27:45.970
in the modern environment.

00:27:45.970 --> 00:27:46.803
That is they're,

00:27:47.640 --> 00:27:51.020
you know, you're supposed
to do things as a couple.

00:27:51.020 --> 00:27:53.150
And if you get too large an age gap,

00:27:53.150 --> 00:27:55.450
then essentially you're
in different cultures.

00:27:56.810 --> 00:27:59.063
You grow up with different songs,

00:28:01.185 --> 00:28:02.840
and if the cultural gap gets too large,

00:28:02.840 --> 00:28:05.214
you don't understand each other.

00:28:05.214 --> 00:28:07.770
So, there are constraints on that,

00:28:07.770 --> 00:28:10.170
but if you look at contexts

00:28:10.170 --> 00:28:12.610
where there are no
constraints of that sort,

00:28:12.610 --> 00:28:17.610
so historically kings,
emperors, despots, et cetera,

00:28:18.600 --> 00:28:21.373
and I'll give one more modern example,

00:28:22.520 --> 00:28:27.520
they basically prefer young,
fertile, attractive females.

00:28:28.150 --> 00:28:29.840
And if they have harems,

00:28:29.840 --> 00:28:31.390
they stock the harems with those,

00:28:31.390 --> 00:28:33.820
and then circulate them out
when they're 30, and so forth.

00:28:33.820 --> 00:28:36.560
And so if you look at marriage systems

00:28:36.560 --> 00:28:38.073
that are unconstrained,

00:28:39.830 --> 00:28:42.240
the preferences are more
likely to be revealed,

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:44.180
or within cultures.

00:28:44.180 --> 00:28:45.440
That is, if you look at men

00:28:45.440 --> 00:28:48.040
who were in a position
to get what they want.

00:28:48.040 --> 00:28:49.500
So as Mick Jagger noted,

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:50.960
