I don't know if he still is,
he's in his seventies now,

00:29:06.890 --> 00:29:09.550
but he was in a position
as was, let's say,

00:29:09.550 --> 00:29:14.010
Rod Stewart, to take another
example, or Leonardo DiCaprio.

00:29:14.010 --> 00:29:16.570
If you were a male who's in a position

00:29:16.570 --> 00:29:18.720
