00:29:18.720 --> 00:29:21.970
potentially available to you,
and you can have your pick,

00:29:21.970 --> 00:29:26.070
then you see that clearer
expression for younger females.

00:29:26.070 --> 00:29:29.880
There was a chart that was
floating around the internet

00:29:29.880 --> 00:29:34.880
of the girlfriends of Leonardo
