when seeking another mate,

01:40:25.740 --> 01:40:27.290
regardless of whether
or not she was married

01:40:27.290 --> 01:40:29.240
or had the children out of wedlock?

01:40:29.240 --> 01:40:30.580
- As a general rule,

01:40:30.580 --> 01:40:32.260
it decreases for mate value,

01:40:32.260 --> 01:40:34.190
because kids with another mate

01:40:34.190 --> 01:40:37.030
