multiple dimensions,

01:40:41.120 --> 01:40:44.640
one of which they're going
to be a cost to the guy,

01:40:44.640 --> 01:40:46.993
because he's going to
have to invest resources,

01:40:48.340 --> 01:40:49.460
time, attention, so forth,

01:40:49.460 --> 01:40:53.560
but also a portion of
her effort and resources

01:40:53.560 --> 01:40:54.950
